Package: mousebreedeR
Type: Package
Title: MousebreedeR assists the user to produce the most efficient breeding schemes for their mouse colonies to attain a certain genotype.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Mike Sportiello
Maintainer: Mike Sportiello <sportiellomike@gmail.com>
Description: Often when breeding mouse colonies for research purposes, several genes need to be in one mouse for an experiment to work. MousebreedeR recommends a breeding scheme to achieve the desired mouse genotype using a novel scoring method to help guide the user.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
